## Goal
Update [prompts.ts](file:///Users/heymarcell/DEV/coloring-generator/test-prompts.ts) to strictly adhere to the "HuePress Coloring Artwork Bible" standards, specifically targeting the 4 complexity levels, line weight specifications, and "Bold & Easy" aesthetic constraints.

